name: Karin Taylor [Playmate June 1996]
description:
A commission from a supporter!

June 1996's Playmate of the month, Karin Taylor. Karin is a former fashion and adult photo model. I tried to capture her late 90's/early 2000's look as well as I could, which was challenging given the old grainy pictures that search engines churned out for me.

The embed has been trained on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models. Due to the limited dataset used for training, some advanced compositions or prompts might be hard to pull off. For this, I recommend transformative prompting, inpainting or ControlNET.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Ko-Fi or Buy Me A Coffee :)
